OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FITV News' Victoria Grimes went to meet
OL,7,FPhill at his school in Birkenhead.
OL,9,FA PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,10,Ffor a whole year in honour of his
OL,11,FGrandfather has been nominated for a
OL,12,FPride of Britain award.
OL,14,FPhill Hayward, from Woodchurch on the
OL,15,FWirral, took on the year-long
OL,16,Fchallenge to raise money for the
OL,17,FAlzheimer's Society, after seeing how
OL,18,Fdementia affected his grandfather Roy
OL,19,FTaylor.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
