OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FPhill said: "Growing up as a small boy
OL,7,Fmy Dad was in the navy in the
OL,8,FFalklands War, so my Grandad was a
OL,9,Ffather figure. He'd pick me up from
OL,10,Fschool and we'd watch football. He was
OL,11,Fmy best friend and an unbelievable
OL,12,Fman."
OL,14,FPhill, who teaches at St Michael and
OL,15,FAll Angels Primary School, had already
OL,16,Fran 10km every day for a year to raise
OL,17,Fmore than #14,000 for mental health
OL,18,Fcharity MIND, and so decided 2024 he
OL,19,Fwould honour Roy by attempting the
OL,20,Ffeat again with an extra added
OL,21,Fchallenge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
