OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FHe said: "I'd done it before in
OL,7,Ftrainers, so I thought it's time to
OL,8,Fpush myself and do it this time in my
OL,9,Fbare feet."
OL,11,FStarting on Sunday 14 July 2024, Phill
OL,12,Fran 10 kilometres every day of the
OL,13,Fyear without any footwear, regardless
OL,14,Fof the weather or his location.
OL,16,F"I did it through all different
OL,17,Fweathers; torrential rain, snow, ice.
OL,18,FWe've had some really hot days too. I
OL,19,Fdid it on birthdays and Christmas," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
