OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FOne of his pupils, 11-year-old Tom,
OL,7,Fsaid: "He's so determined to help
OL,8,Fpeople, and sometimes I feel sorry for
OL,9,Fhim because he's been out in the snow
OL,10,Fand the rain. He's really inspired me
OL,11,Fto help people with disabilities and
OL,12,Fjust be a nice person."
OL,14,FTom's sister Sicily, eight, added:
OL,15,F"Some people see him as just our PE
OL,16,Fteacher but he's also inspirational
OL,17,Fand determined and someone who just
OL,18,Fkeeps going."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
