OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FPhill finished his final 10km on 14
OL,7,FJuly 2025, and was joined by some of
OL,8,Fhis pupils for his final lap.
OL,10,FSadly, one person who couldn't be
OL,11,Fthere was his Grandfather Roy who had
OL,12,Fdied just weeks before his final run.
OL,14,FPhill said: "It was really difficult.
OL,15,FI sort of became a father figure to
OL,16,Fhim as he forgot who he was, and where
OL,17,Fhe lived, and who certain people were.
OL,19,F"But he never forgot who I was, and
OL,20,Fthat meant we could keep that
OL,21,Frelationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
