OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax     F397A1758024506
OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,F"Until you live with it you don't
OL,7,Frealise just how hard it is, and part
OL,8,Fof the reason I did this challenge was
OL,9,Fto raise awareness and help find a
OL,10,Fcure."
OL,12,FAfter completing his challenge, Phill
OL,13,Fwas nominated for the Pride of Britain
OL,14,FFundraiser of the Year Award by a
OL,15,Fnumber of people who had heard his
OL,16,Fstory, including his head teacher
OL,17,FSusan Ralph.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
