OL,3,CThe PE teacher who ran 10km every day
OL,4,Cfor a year to honour his Grandfather
OL,6,FShe said: "We have school values here,
OL,7,Fand he just lives and breathes them.
OL,8,FHe's the most humble man, so I knew he
OL,9,Fwould hate it when I nominated him,
OL,10,Fbut he deserves to have his praises
OL,11,Fsung."
OL,13,FWhen asked what it meant to be
OL,14,Fnominated, Phill said: "I can't
OL,15,Fbelieve it really. Things like this
OL,16,Fdon't happen to people like me, and
OL,17,Fpeople in this area. I'm totally
OL,18,Foverwhelmed."
